// Wave 2 piece N: Execute E2E demo. Instant-kills target if their hp
// is below threshold. Lowers to EffectOp::Execute{hp_threshold: 20.0}.
//
// Conditional-emit path: the verb's `when` clause gates on target.hp <
// threshold; on fire it emits a Defeated event the new ApplyDefeat
// chronicle drains via agents.set_alive(c, false). Distinct from the
// existing inline Defeated emit in ApplyDamage's hp<=0 branch — both
// idempotently set alive=false.

ability Reap {
    target: enemy
    range: 5.0
    cooldown: 2s
    hint: damage

    execute 20
}
